Package business

Class Person

java.lang.Object
business.Person
public class Person extends Object
Class Person that includes name, geographic data, date of birth, phone number, email, health plan beneficiary number, bank account number, date of start on the company, department, url of the image, personal code of a person and a increment variable to designate a counter.
Version:
3.0
Author:
